---
const site = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_SITE;
const base = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_BASE;
const site2 = Astro.site;
const path = Astro.site?.pathname;
---

<div
  class="h-svh md:h-screen snap-start w-full px-5 py-20 md:px-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-evenly gap-8"
>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-5">
    <h2
      class="bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary to-primary bg-clip-text text-transparent font-bold text-5xl md:text-6xl text-center"
    >
      Cursos Publicados
    </h2>
    <p class="max-w-2xl text-center text-accent/85">
      Aqu√≠ puedes ver los cursos que hemos publicado en nuestro blog.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-9 w-full max-w-6xl">
    <div class="card bg-base-100 w-96 shadow-sm">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Card Title</h2>
        <p>
          A card component has a figure, a body part, and inside body there are
          title and actions parts
        </p>
      </div>
      <figure>
        <img
          src="https://img.daisyui.com/images/stock/photo-1606107557195-0e29a4b5b4aa.webp"
          alt="Shoes"
        />
      </figure>
    </div>
    <ul>
      <li><a class="link" href="dogs/clifford">Link1</a></li>
      <li><a class="link" href="dogs/rover">Link2</a></li>
      <li><a class="link" href="dogs/spot">Link3</a></li>
      <li><a class="link" href="dogs/curso-d">Link4</a></li>
      <li><a class="link" href="dogs/curso-e">Link5</a></li>
      <li><a class="link" href="dogs/curso-f">Link6</a></li>
      <li><a class="link" href="dogs/curso-g">Link7</a></li>
      <li><a class="link" href="dogs/curso-h">Link8</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Site: {site}</p>
    <p>Base: {base}</p>
    <p>Site2: {site2}</p>
    <p>Path: {path}</p>
  </div>
</div>
